<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulm</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, welche Fürsten, Grafen, Herren und Bischöfe sich derzeit in Nürnberg aufhalten, um den Streit zwischen Herzog Ludwig VII. von Bayern-Ingolstadt mit Markgraf Friedrich I. von Brandenburg und Herzog Heinrich XVI. von Bayern-Landshut zu schlichten, und, dass sich Pfalzgraf Ludwig III. bei Rhein und Herzog Heinrich bald in Amberg treffen wollen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_21" id="9v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_21_r1l1">Vlm </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_21_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Als vns ewr weiſheit <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von 
<del rend="strikethrough"> des tag </del> der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l3">fürſten 
<del rend="strikethrough">vve </del> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> wegen die <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> hie ſein . <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l4">vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> . vnd tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> cʒuvviſſen daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l5"><expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> hie ſein . die durchleuhtigen . hochwirdigen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l6">hochgeporen fürſten . mitnamen vnſer herren hercʒog </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l7">Ludwig von der Pfalcʒ / der Marggraf von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l8">die Byſſchöf von Bamberg . vvircʒburg <expan>Regenſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> Eẏſtet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l9">vnd Speyr . hercʒog Ludwig von Beyrn Graf cʒu Mortanj </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l10">hercʒog Ernſt vnd wilhelm <expan>geprüde<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd hercʒog <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>
<del rend="strikethrough">s</del></expan></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l11">von Beẏern . Burggraf <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> vnd ſüſt vil Grafen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l12">vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . vnd vernemen vvie ſie teydingen von ſölcher </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l14">Spenn wegen 
<del rend="strikethrough">die </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_21_line_1573113665415_439">die </ab></add> <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_21_line_1573113669424_444">den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Marggrafe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l15">von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> vnd hercʒog <expan>Ludwig<ex>en</ex></expan> Grafen cʒu Mortanj 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſind </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l16">vnd auch <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hercʒog <expan>Ludwig<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> vettern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l17">hercʒog <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Beyern . 
<del rend="strikethrough">auch von ſolcher Spenn </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l18">
<del rend="strikethrough">wegen . die <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jn </del> ſind . vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l19">vvie . der <expan>obgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> herre hercʒog Ludwig von der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l20">Pfalcʒ als hewte hinauf gen <expan>Amb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>reyte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> wer </del> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l24">dohin 
<add><ab facs="#facs_21_line_1573113833909_467">auch </ab></add> der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> hercʒog <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_21_line_1573113839198_472">cʒu Jm </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> auch </del> <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> werde vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l25">alſo verſteen vvir vns daʒ ſie noch etvvielang hıe <expan>bleıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l26"><expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan> ob ſie aber icht anderr ſache cʒeſchicken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_21_r1l27">des vviſſen vvir niht / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvo etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Corp<ex>or</ex>ıs</expan> xpi </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_21" id="9v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
